📌 Loan Approval Predictor (Streamlit + ML)

A simple Machine Learning web app built with Streamlit that predicts whether a loan will be approved or rejected based on applicant financial details.

🚀 Live Demo

(Add later if you deploy on Streamlit Cloud)
https://your-app-link.streamlit.app

📊 Features
💳 Loan approval prediction (ML model)
📈 Uses financial & credit features
⚡ Real-time prediction via Streamlit UI
📉 Risk-based decision output
🧠 Trained on structured loan dataset
📊 Clean and user-friendly interface with input guidelines
🧠 Input Features Used
Applicant Income
Coapplicant Income
Age
Dependents
Credit Score
Existing Loans
DTI Ratio
Savings
Collateral Value
Loan Amount
Loan Term
