⚙️ Installation
1️⃣ Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/your-username/loan-predictor.git
cd loan-predictor
2️⃣ Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
3️⃣ Run app
streamlit run app.py
🚀 How It Works
User enters financial details
Data is preprocessed (encoding + scaling)
ML model predicts approval/rejection
Result is displayed instantly in UI
⚠️ Dataset Guidelines

Use realistic values:

Income: 2000 – 20000
Credit Score: 550 – 799
Loan Amount: 1000 – 40000
DTI Ratio: 0.1 – 0.6
